_:N91359c67eccc44af80f878d4993a7fc1 <http://schema.org/name> "The Rt Hon Nick Thomas–Symonds MP" .
_:N91359c67eccc44af80f878d4993a7fc1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Nick Thomas–Symonds was appointed Paymaster General and Minister for the Cabinet Office (Minister for the Constitution and European Union Relations) at the Cabinet Office on 8 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Torfaen in May 2015.</p>\n" .
